## Contact Form — Spec Lengkap

### Fields
```python
class ContactForm(forms.Form):
    name    = forms.CharField(max_length=100)
    email   = forms.EmailField()
    phone   = forms.CharField(max_length=20, required=False)
    subject = forms.CharField(max_length=200)
    message = forms.CharField(widget=forms.Textarea)
```

### Validasi Dua Layer (WAJIB)

**Client-side (real-time JS):**
- Validasi saat user mengetik (`input` event)
- Visual feedback: border merah (error) / hijau (valid) per field
- Pesan error spesifik di bawah field
- Phone: validasi format Indonesia (08xx / +62xx)
- Disable tombol Submit jika ada error

**Server-side (Django Forms):**
- `clean_email()` — format valid
- `clean_phone()` — sanitize + validasi format Indonesia
- `clean_message()` — minimal 20 karakter
- `{% csrf_token %}` wajib

### Notifikasi
- Email via Django `send_mail` + SMTP Gmail
- WhatsApp via Twilio (Phase 2, opsional)
- Success: konfirmasi animated + form reset
- Error: pesan spesifik per field

