## Git Conventions

```
feat: add contact form with real-time validation
fix: correct static files path
style: update hero typewriter timing
refactor: split settings into base/local/production
docs: add setup instructions to README
test: add unit tests for ContactForm validation
chore: update requirements.txt
```

Branch: `main` (prod) ← `develop` ← `feature/nama-fitur`

---

## What Cursor MUST NOT Do

- Install CSS framework tanpa konfirmasi
- Install JS framework tanpa konfirmasi
- Taruh business logic di templates
- Hardcode environment variables
- Skip migration setelah ubah models
- Commit `db.sqlite3`, `.env`, atau `media/`

---

## Pre-Commit Checklist

- [ ] `python manage.py check --deploy` lulus
- [ ] Semua form punya `{% csrf_token %}`
- [ ] Tidak ada secret di kode
- [ ] Migration sudah dibuat
- [ ] Static files pakai `{% static %}`
- [ ] Type hints ada di semua fungsi baru
